---
---
<section id="limitations" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="limitations-wrapper glass-panel">
      <div class="warning-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3Z"/><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="9" y2="13"/><line x1="12" x2="12.01" y1="17" y2="17"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="limitations-content">
        <h2>Important Limitations</h2>
        <p class="intro-text">CropCheckUp is an AI-assisted screening tool. Results depend highly on image quality, lighting, leaf visibility, and whether the condition exists in the trained labels.</p>
        
        <div class="rules-grid">
          <div class="rule-item">
            <span class="rule-bullet"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.5 4h-5L7 7H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v9a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-3l-2.5-3z"/><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="3"/></svg></span>
            <p>Use a clear image of one leaf, properly focused and well-lit.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rule-item">
            <span class="rule-bullet"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="4.93" x2="19.07" y1="4.93" y2="19.07"/></svg></span>
            <p>Avoid blur, heavy shadows, and cluttered backgrounds with multiple plants.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rule-item">
            <span class="rule-bullet"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10 2v7.31"/><path d="M14 9.3V1.99"/><path d="M8.5 2h7"/><path d="M14 9.3a6.5 6.5 0 1 1-4 0"/><path d="M5.52 16h12.96"/></svg></span>
            <p>Always confirm serious crop issues with a certified agriculture expert.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rule-item">
            <span class="rule-bullet"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/></svg></span>
            <p>The app can only classify conditions within its supported 68-label dataset.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .limitations-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-warning);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .limitations-wrapper {
      flex-direction: row;
      gap: var(--space-xl);
      align-items: center;
    }
  }

  .limitations-wrapper::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  
  .limitations-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .warning-icon {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-m);
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.4));
    color: var(--color-warning);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    animation: pulseWarning 3s infinite alternate ease-in-out;
  }

  @keyframes pulseWarning {
    0% { filter: drop-shadow(0 0 15px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3)); transform: scale(1); }
    100% { filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.6)); transform: scale(1.05); }
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .warning-icon {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    
    .warning-icon svg {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
    }
  }

  .limitations-content {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .limitations-content h2 {
    color: var(--color-warning);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-s);
  }

  .intro-text {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .rules-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-m);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .rules-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  .rule-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-m);
    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
    padding: var(--space-l);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  }

  .rule-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    border-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), 0 0 15px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1);
  }

  .rule-bullet {
    margin-top: -2px;
    color: var(--color-warning);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.4));
  }

  .rule-item p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
</style>
